@startuml
!include ../../styles/plantuml-theme.puml

left to right direction
title FIG-11-06. Horizon Bank Payment Observability View

skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #333333
  BackgroundColor #F7F9FB
}
skinparam component {
  BorderColor #333333
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
}
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.3

rectangle "Horizon Bank Payment Systems" as Systems {
  component "Horizon Digital\nChannels" as Channels
  component "Payments\nPlatform" as Payments
  component "Financial Crime\nPlatform" as FinancialCrime
  component "Enterprise Integration\nPlatform" as Integration
  queue "Event Platform" as EventPlatform
  database "Core Deposit\nSystem" as CoreDeposit
}

rectangle "Telemetry Signals" as Signals {
  component "Traces" as Traces
  component "Metrics" as Metrics
  component "Logs" as Logs
}

component "OpenTelemetry\nCollector" as Collector
component "Filtering and\nSensitive-Data Redaction" as Redaction
database "Observability\nBackends" as Backends
rectangle "Payment Service Indicators\n\npayment submission rate\nscreening latency\nposting-confirmation delay\nfailed-payment rate\nevent backlog\ncustomer-status update lag" as Indicators
component "Payment Operations\nDashboards" as Dashboards
component "Alert Routing" as Alerts

actor "Operations\nTeam" as Ops
actor "Service\nOwner" as Owner

Channels -[#2D6A4F,dotted]-> Traces : request flow
Payments -[#2D6A4F,dotted]-> Traces : payment trace
Payments -[#2D6A4F,dotted]-> Metrics : submission and failure rates
FinancialCrime -[#2D6A4F,dotted]-> Metrics : screening timing
Integration -[#2D6A4F,dotted]-> Logs : posting integration logs
EventPlatform -[#2D6A4F,dotted]-> Metrics : backlog and lag
CoreDeposit -[#2D6A4F,dotted]-> Logs : posting confirmations

Traces --> Collector : telemetry
Metrics --> Collector : telemetry
Logs --> Collector : telemetry
Collector --> Redaction : process and filter
Redaction --> Backends : exported telemetry
Backends --> Indicators : derive service indicators
Indicators --> Dashboards : displayed
Indicators --> Alerts : thresholds
Dashboards --> Ops : monitor service
Dashboards --> Owner : service health view
Alerts --> Ops : actionable alerts
Alerts --> Owner : service-impact alerts

legend bottom
Dotted arrows show telemetry emission from payment systems.
Filtering and sensitive-data redaction happen before telemetry reaches shared backends.
Dashboards support investigation; alert routing supports action.
endlegend
@enduml
